  "optimization_notes": "Root cause: remaining hot-path cost is dominated by startup work that is not proportional to output, especially unconditional mmap/prefetch and dictionary loading before confirming any qualifying 2023 rows. Strategy category C (work elimination) with plan restructuring: first read only the ddate zonemap to determine overlap, immediately return empty output when no blocks overlap, defer loading all large columns, anti-join index, and tag/version dictionaries until survivors exist, and avoid whole-column prefetch in hot runs so memory traffic is paid only for blocks and rows that can contribute to final groups.",
